2026-01-04 02:38:35,084 - RootCauseAnalysis - INFO - [State Update] {"hypotheses_summary": "Redis on aiops-k8s-06 is the root cause due to node_filesystem_usage_rate exhaustion affecting cartservice. Concurrently, significant internal exceptions are occurring in AdService impacting frontend accessibility.", "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error: code = Unknown desc\",\n    \"failed to retrieve ads\",\n    \"ThrowException\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception\",\n    \"java.lang.Error\",\n    \"Injected error\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"adservice--stress\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Repeated instances of 'AdService-getRandomAds-exception' and 'Injected error' indicating internal exceptions\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs from adservice show '[Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException]', and frequent 'java.lang.Error: Injected error'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failure to retrieve ads due to possible downstream service issue\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Errors like 'rpc error: code = Unknown desc = failed to retrieve ads' are logged by frontend service when calling adservice\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_filesystem_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased significantly, which might have affected memory availability for pods running on it.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes reduced from 10002227200.0 to 8687095808.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly, indicating potential latency issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 8948.49 to 60370.8.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate increased, possibly causing storage bottlenecks.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate increased significantly during the fault period.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过分析从 2025-06-10T06:10:40Z 到 2025-06-10T06:31:40Z 的调用链数据，我们发现了多个异常的调用链条和显著的延迟。\n\n### 异常调用链识别\n以下是主要的异常调用链和其特征：\n\n1. **Frontend 到 CheckoutService**\n   - 异常延迟：约 2 倍标准延迟\n   - 调用关系：`frontend->checkoutservice`\n   - 异常发生频次：非常高\n\n2. **CartService 和 Redis**\n   - 异常延迟：迅速增长到正常延迟的约 30 倍\n   - 调用关系：`cartservice->redis`\n   - 异常发生频次：1 次事件\n\n3. **CheckoutService 到 CartService**\n   - 异常延迟显著增加\n   - 调用关系：`checkoutservice->cartservice`\n   - 异常发生频次：多次\n\n4. **CheckoutService 到 EmailService**\n   - 异常延迟约增加 2 倍\n   - 调用关系：`checkoutservice->emailservice`\n   - 异常发生频次：1 次事件\n\n5. **ShippingService 延迟增加**\n   - 调用关系：`checkoutservice->shippingservice`\n   - 异常发生频次：1 次事件\n\n### 状态代码分析\n- **`AdService` 错误状态码 2：** 高频出现\n  - 异常路径：`frontend->AdService`\n  - 频次非常高，表明存在连接问题或服务不可用的情况\n\n### 延迟分析结果\n- 许多服务出现超过正常平均延迟数倍的情况，尤其是`cartservice`和`checkoutservice`\n- 其中`cartservice`和`redis`之间的请求延迟显著增加，可能导致上下游服务的延迟\n\n### 根因定位\n从拓扑结构推测，`redis`的快速延迟增长可能是一个关键的瓶颈，对`cartservice`的影响十分显著。而频繁的`AdService`错误状态表明了潜在的连接问题。可能的网络问题使得请求无法顺利进行。\n\n### 建议\n- 检查`redis`配置优化延迟问题。\n- 深入分析`AdService`的连接问题并确认是否存在服务故障。\n- 针对较高延迟服务进行负载测试以鉴定具体瓶颈位置。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"frontend->AdService\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟增长\",\n      \"evidence\": \"anomaly_avg_duration约为正常情况的30倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"频繁错误状态码\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态码2出现次数高\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"可能受下游影响导致延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个Service调用链中延迟显著增加\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n上述分析基于当前异常调用链数据得到的结论，建议结合其他监控数据和历史表现做进一步深入调查以确认问题根因。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "9b0d8a50-187", "component": "redis-cart-0", "reason": "node_filesystem_usage_rate spike causing cartservice latency issues", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(aiops-k8s-06)", "observation": "node_filesystem_usage_rate increased from baseline levels to 82% during fault window."}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceAnalysis(9b0d8a50-187)", "observation": "High latency observed in cartservice->redis calls correlating to filesystem usage."}, {"step": 3, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "redis-cart-0 identified on affected node aiops-k8s-06."}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
